name: Serina
content:
Serina was a Human female smuggler who operated out of the city of Tyrena on the planet Corellia during the time of the Galactic Civil War.
Serina was a non-player character in the 2003 video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online roleplaying game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011. Serina was added to the game along with the smuggling missions introduced with the "Chapter 3" update, released on September 27, 2006.
